      <title>RabbitMQ安装和基本概念</title>
      <link>https://solaim.github.io/posts/rabbitmq%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E5%92%8C%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E6%A6%82%E5%BF%B5/</link>
